{"tid":1716824,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港交所：逾140隻ETF在港上市買賣","createTime":"2019-11-13T12:37:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T10:51:58.000Z","uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5abe803a1c17406fbffe62d0dae1470a14bac23b","tid":1716824,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:37:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491632-20191112.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491632-20191112.htm&d=eC9RRsiBNQJpYHZqEQI0QhZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=b0374a7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491632-20191112.htm&h=2cbdc4f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491632-20191112.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n香港交易所數字顯示，目前超過140隻交易所買賣基金（ETF）在本港上市買賣，每日成交額50億元，管理資產金額超過3000億元。近年，ETF發行商推出槓桿及反向產品、主動型ETF、貨幣市場ETF及一系列主題投資產品。<br />\n<br />\n交易所計劃明年推出更多ETF市場提升措施，預期將有助增加市場流動性及縮窄ETF產品價差。<br />\n<br />\n港交所指出，今日是香港ETF市場發展20周年。香港ETF市場已成為亞洲區最多元化市場之一，讓投資者以不同投資策略涉足全球股票、固定收益及商品市場。<br />\n<br />\n交易所亦與業界合作，推出多項市場提升措施，包括獲豁免ETF交易的印花稅、優化特許證券商計劃，容許更多流通量提供者進入香港市場、推出補購豁免協助莊家為市場提供流通量等。"},{"pid":"1867ec5a5c2b8f6308d133951b80dc1ae439f6fa","tid":1716824,"uid":303244,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:40:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1eb6cb1873a230141fff95571df8d810e3a82e5","tid":1716824,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"077284ec2db1253b71185cdc2df4004b3110ad90","tid":1716824,"uid":43016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:58:54.000Z","msg":"垃圾香港ETF有交投既都唔知有冇30隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb0052d982ac2070f0f2e9f8cdf68e928783f4e","tid":1716824,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:00:32.000Z","msg":"仆你個街 得幾隻見得人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"379661c9d062d54e004290092fbcb9ffd8452bcf","tid":1716824,"uid":89225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:02:14.000Z","msg":"垃9圾。明明ETF可以好好攪大佢。淨係去攪埋d衍生野<br />\nD ETF成交細到.."},{"pid":"98007027768650ac5e6c4722866655e4b7b321ae","tid":1716824,"uid":34976,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"379661c9d062d54e004290092fbcb9ffd8452bcf","tid":1716824,"uid":89225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:02:14.000Z","msg":"垃9圾。明明ETF可以好好攪大佢。淨係去攪埋d衍生野<br />\nD ETF成交細到.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:03:50.000Z","msg":"香港人唔鍾意買ETF，買得都當賭錢<br />\n去美國就唔同，真係買ETF黎廣泛投資，買SPY/VOO/QQQ/VTI黎投資指數不知幾好"},{"pid":"c8da5109493b451f975b8d13f33e92fbef39181c","tid":1716824,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:08:02.000Z","msg":"個個牛熊證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00fc90209dac6d9e8f607a337d185f2ea203795","tid":1716824,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:10:51.000Z","msg":"如果比我有幾球<br />\n投資一隻2800夠哂皮<br />\n唔考慮其他ETF"},{"pid":"64b78948612b987f5e1fe820fbd5389ae231c7fd","tid":1716824,"uid":67362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:13:59.000Z","msg":"牛熊ETF<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b378cb396270413931e1c084b619e40972ce15c1","tid":1716824,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:14:37.000Z","msg":"報警已經係死罪"},{"pid":"6ec47a31fc099bb9eeb50087630821286b76146f","tid":1716824,"uid":198536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:35:40.000Z","msg":"7500 7200<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma